    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies. This unit benefits from a documented VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, addressing critical platform vulnerabilities. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with precision, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. While showing minor cosmetic patina expected of a driven machine, the suspension geometry remains true and the power delivery is linear and visceral. A purist\u2019s specification for those valuing mechanical integrity and tactile feedback.",
